gurmukhi: kYsy kY Agh gihE kYsy kY ACl CilE kYsy kY AByd BydXo AlK lKwieE hY
transliteration: Kaisay Kai Agah Gahiao Kaisay Kai Achhal Chhaliao , Kaisay Kai Abhayd Bhaydayo Alakh Lakhaaiao Hai ?
translation: O friend! how have you acquired the Lord who cannot be seized? How have you tricked Him who cannot be deceived? How have you known His secret whose secret is not revealable? How have you realised Him who cannot be accessed?

gurmukhi: kYsy kY ApyK pyKXo kYsy kY AgV giVXo kYsy kY ApXo pIE Ajr jrwieE hY
transliteration: Kaisay Kai Apaykh Paykhayo Kaisay Kai Agarh Garhiyo , Kaisay Kai Apayo Peeao Ajar Jaraaiao Hai ?

gurmukhi: AdBuq gq Ascrj ibsm Aiq kYsy kY Apwr inrwDwr TihrwieE hY ]648]
transliteration: Adabhout Gat Asacharaj Bisam Ati , Kaisay Kai Apaar Niraadhaar Tthahiraaiao Hai ?648?
translation: The Lord whose every aspect is so amazing, wondrous and beyond comprehension, how have you lodged Him in your heart who is infinite and without form?  (648)
